- Help us, Challenge Man.

808
00:29:40,359 --> 00:29:41,858
- Challenge Man.
- "Airplane" is...

809
00:29:41,859 --> 00:29:44,858
"Airplane" is a good song for you.

810
00:29:44,859 --> 00:29:47,368
