829
00:30:29,109 --> 00:30:30,409
- Good.
- I like the look in his eyes.

830
00:30:31,409 --> 00:30:33,509
Gosh, it's artistic.

831
00:30:33,679 --> 00:30:34,709
Nice.

832
00:30:35,009 --> 00:30:37,748
