846
00:31:00,609 --> 00:31:02,509
That part was good.

847
00:31:03,239 --> 00:31:04,309
Nice.

848
00:31:05,039 --> 00:31:06,878
- This is great.
- All right.

849
00:31:06,879 --> 00:31:08,108
