- Sure.

852
00:31:12,079 --> 00:31:14,519
- Help me, Challenge Man.
- Challenge Man.

853
00:31:14,919 --> 00:31:16,488
Joon is the best.

854
00:31:16,489 --> 00:31:17,688
- Challenge Man.
- Challenge Man.

855
00:31:17,689 --> 00:31:21,459
