- It's chilly.

909
00:33:14,082 --> 00:33:15,882
- It got cold.
- No, it's okay.

910
00:33:16,185 --> 00:33:17,554
- Please eat this.
- "Eat this?"

911
00:33:17,579 --> 00:33:18,609
No.

912
00:33:18,919 --> 00:33:21,689
Se Yoon loves to eat, but he doesn't eat parkas.

913
00:33:22,049 --> 00:33:23,919
- Because he has many layers on?
- He does.

914
00:33:24,179 --> 00:33:25,179
Okay.

915
00:33:25,180 --> 00:33:26,989
What if I start talking like him by putting this on?

916
00:33:28,149 --> 00:33:29,918
Hold on. Is it a magic suit?

917
00:33:29,919 --> 00:33:31,058
