953
00:34:36,559 --> 00:34:38,118
- Can't it be "telephone call?"
- Call?

954
00:34:38,119 --> 00:34:39,119
- Telephone call.
- Telephone call.

955
00:34:39,120 --> 00:34:40,128
- It has four characters in Korean.
- It has four characters in Korean.

956
00:34:40,129 --> 00:34:41,558
That counts.

957
00:34:41,559 --> 00:34:43,959
It's not a 4-character idiom. It's just a 4-character word.

958
00:34:44,259 --> 00:34:45,629
Please give it to us if it's funny.

959
00:34:45,799 --> 00:34:48,329
If everyone laughs their head off, we'll give it to you.

960
