990
00:35:38,749 --> 00:35:41,619
- Let's get kimchi.
- We're picking up the momentum.

991
00:35:41,949 --> 00:35:44,689
My mind is completely blank. I can't think.

992
00:35:44,819 --> 00:35:45,889
The Netherlands.

993
00:35:46,059 --> 00:35:47,288
- Amsterdam.
- Okay.

994
00:35:47,289 --> 00:35:48,388
