995
00:35:48,389 --> 00:35:50,059
- Jong Min will get the times table.
- All right.

996
00:35:51,859 --> 00:35:53,229
After being slapped in Jongno...

997
00:35:53,799 --> 00:35:55,028
- Cheongnyangni...
- Wrong.

998
00:35:55,029 --> 00:35:56,029
You jerk.

999
00:35:56,529 --> 00:35:58,039
Letting off steam at Han River.

1000
00:35:58,599 --> 00:36:00,639
What were you going to say? After being slapped in Jongno...

1001
00:36:01,009 --> 00:36:02,939
